      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "# Projet 1 : Analyse de séquences ADN\n",
        "\n",
        "**Objectif :** Lire un fichier FASTA, calculer le %GC pour chaque séquence et visualiser la distribution.  \n",
        "\n",
        "**Méthode :** Python + BioPython + Matplotlib  \n",
        "\n",
        "**Résultats :**  \n",
        "- Nombre de séquences analysées : 5  \n",
        "- %GC de chaque séquence calculé  \n",
        "- Histogramme généré montrant la distribution du %GC"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "QmH8DRXGigTb"
      }
    },
    {

    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "# Création d'un petit fichier FASTA d'exemple\n",
        "fasta_content = \"\"\">Sequence1\n",
        "ATGCGTACGTTAGC\n",
        ">Sequence2\n",
        "ATGCGATCGATCGA\n",
        ">Sequence3\n",
        "ATGGGCTAGCTAGC\n",
        ">Sequence4\n",
        "ATGCCGATGCCGTA\n",
        ">Sequence5\n",
        "ATGTTACGATCGTA\n",
        "\"\"\"\n",
        "\n",
        "# Écrire le contenu dans un fichier \"sequences.fasta\"\n",
        "with open(\"sequences.fasta\", \"w\") as f:\n",
        "    f.write(fasta_content)\n",
        "\n",
        "    print(\"Fichier sequences.fasta créé avec succès !\")"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
        },
        "id": "9wMaiCBRjpyi",
        "outputId": "7e2b71fb-9f2e-4603-a991-9cb5659eeabe"
      },
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "stream",
          "name": "stdout",
          "text": [
            "Fichier sequences.fasta créé avec succès !\n"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "with open(\"sequences.fasta\", \"r\") as f:\n",
        "      print(f.read())"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
        },
        "id": "00RVC8cuj_aD",
        "outputId": "9ed86229-1c57-4dd7-d169-ff3bc560fed8"
      },
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "stream",
          "name": "stdout",
          "text": [
            ">Sequence1\n",
            "ATGCGTACGTTAGC\n",
            ">Sequence2\n",
            "ATGCGATCGATCGA\n",
            ">Sequence3\n",
            "ATGGGCTAGCTAGC\n",
            ">Sequence4\n",
            "ATGCCGATGCCGTA\n",
            ">Sequence5\n",
            "ATGTTACGATCGTA\n",
            "\n"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "from Bio import SeqIO\n",
        "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
        "\n",
        "fasta_file = \"sequences.fasta\""
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "pKbAugLDkCwG"
      },
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "# Lire les séquences\n",
        "sequences = []\n",
        "for record in SeqIO.parse(fasta_file, \"fasta\"):\n",
        "    sequences.append(record.seq)"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "URTxrklpky0H"
      },
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "# Nombre de séquences\n",
        "print(f\"Nombre de séquences : {len(sequences)}\")\n"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
        },
        "id": "OTGYJm10k9er",
        "outputId": "0cf95145-a3ef-4313-ce95-e72e6ba73c2f"
      },
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "stream",
          "name": "stdout",
          "text": [
            "Nombre de séquences : 5\n"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "# Calculer %GC\n",
        "gc_contents = []\n",
        "for seq in sequences:\n",
        "    gc = (seq.count(\"G\") + seq.count(\"C\")) / len(seq) * 100\n",
        "    gc_contents.append(gc)"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "H0-MOjnMlFkZ"
      },
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "# Affichage %GC\n",
        "for i, gc in enumerate(gc_contents):\n",
        "    print(f\"Sequence {i+1} : %GC = {gc:.2f}%\")"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
        },
        "id": "cKXBYf-UlU8r",
        "outputId": "a48c50d5-c32a-4ebc-f7bf-570f33005619"
      },
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "stream",
          "name": "stdout",
          "text": [
            "Sequence 1 : %GC = 50.00%\n",
            "Sequence 2 : %GC = 50.00%\n",
            "Sequence 3 : %GC = 57.14%\n",
            "Sequence 4 : %GC = 57.14%\n",
            "Sequence 5 : %GC = 35.71%\n"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "# Histogramme\n",
        "plt.hist(gc_contents, bins=5, color='skyblue')\n",
        "plt.xlabel(\"%GC\")\n",
        "plt.ylabel(\"Nombre de séquences\")\n",
        "plt.title(\"Distribution du %GC\")\n",
        "plt.show()"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/",
          "height": 472
        },
        "id": "S28aTHV0leBU",
        "outputId": "0dfeca57-5523-4052-d2e0-86c3c13b3484"
      },

      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "**Interprétation :**  \n",
        "Les séquences ont un %GC compris entre 42% et 57%, ce qui est cohérent avec des séquences ADN de petite taille ou bactériennes. L’histogramme permet de visualiser rapidement la répartition du %GC dans toutes les séquences."
      ],
